                              <h4>About This App</h4>
                              <hr />
                              <p>BrokeGamer is an app designed for crowdsourced video game deal apps. Users can search the database for video games, search for all the current deals, post new deals, post reviews, and create a wishlist of games they want. This app was created using HTML, CSS, Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, jQuery, Angular, Git, and SQL.</p>
                              
                           </div>
                       </div>

